verses.roman:
ei vijayā-daśamīte haila ei rīti
tāṅhāke puchiyā tāṅra karāiha pratīti

synonyms: ei vijayā-daśamīte—on the previous Vijayā-daśamī day; haila—there was; ei rīti—such an incident; tāṅhāke—unto her; puchiyā—asking; tāṅra—her; karāiha—make; pratīti—belief.
translation: "Such an incident took place on the last Vijayā-daśamī day. You can ask her about this incident and thus make her believe that I actually go there."
